title: Super Bowl 2026: Patriots' battered and bruised OL is in for its toughest test in a postseason full of them

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Super Bowl 2026: Patriots' battered and bruised OL is in for its toughest test in a postseason full of them
sources.description: New England has been dominated up front by its three playoff opponents, and still found a way to win. If the O-line can do it one more time, we might be in for a surprise result on Sunday.
